#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:8
msgid ""
"The *algorithm id* is displayed when you hover over the algorithm in the "
"Processing Toolbox. The *parameter dictionary* provides the parameter NAMEs "
"and values. See :ref:`processing_console` for details on how to run "
"processing algorithms from the Python console."
msgstr ""
"*ID algoritma* se prikazuje kada pređete mišem preko algoritma u kutiji sa "
"alatkama Obrade. *Rečnik parametara* daje NAZIVe i vrednosti parametara. "
"Pogledajte :ref:`processing_console` za detalje o pokretanju algoritama "
"obrade iz Python konzole."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:73
msgid "Extract projection"
msgstr "Izdvajanje projekcije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:74
msgid ""
"Extracts the projection of a raster file and writes it into a *world* file "
"with extension :file:`.wld`."
msgstr ""
"Izdvaja projekciju rasterske datoteke i upisuje je u *world* datoteku sa "
"ekstenzijom :file:`.wld`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:77
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL srsinfo utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdalsrsinfo.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam izveden je iz `GDAL srsinfo alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdalsrsinfo.html>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:94
msgid "**Input file**"
msgstr "**Ulazna datoteka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:97
msgid ""
"Input raster The raster layer has to be file based, as the algorithm uses "
"the path to the raster file as the location of the generated :file:`.wld` "
"file. Using a non-file raster layer will lead to an error."
msgstr ""
"Ulazni raster. Rasterski sloj mora biti zasnovan na datoteci, jer algoritam "
"koristi putanju do rasterske datoteke kao lokaciju generisane :file:`.wld` "
"datoteke. Korišćenje rasterskog sloja koji nije zasnovan na datoteci dovešće"
" do greške."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:102
