msgstr "Podrazumevano: False"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:107
msgid ""
"If this is activated a :file:`.prj` file containing the projection "
"information is also created."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ovo aktivirano, pravi se i :file:`.prj` datoteka sa podacima o "
"projekciji."

