#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:271
msgid "**Georeferenced extents of output file to be created**"
msgstr "**Georeferencirani obuhvat izlazne datoteke koja se pravi**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:274
msgid "``TARGET_EXTENT``"
msgstr "``TARGET_EXTENT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:275
msgid "[extent]"
msgstr "[obuhvat]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:276
msgid ""
"Sets the georeferenced extent of the output file to be created (in the "
":guilabel:`Target CRS` by default. In the :guilabel:`CRS of the target "
"raster extent`, if specified)."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja georeferencirani obuhvat izlazne datoteke koja se pravi "
"(podrazumevano u :guilabel:`Ciljni CRS`. U :guilabel:`CRS ciljnog obuhvata "
"rastera`, ako je zadat)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:3
msgid "Available methods are:"
msgstr "Dostupni metodi su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:5
msgid ""
"Calculate from layer…: uses extent of a layer loaded in the current project"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz sloja…: koristi obuhvat sloja učitanog u tekućem projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:6
msgid ""
"Calculate from layout map…: uses extent of a :ref:`layout map item "
"<layout_map_item>` in the active project"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz karte rasporeda…: koristi obuhvat :ref:`stavke karte u "
"rasporedu <layout_map_item>` u aktivnom projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:8
msgid ""
"Calculate from bookmark…: uses extent of a saved :ref:`bookmark "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz obeleživača…: koristi obuhvat sačuvanog :ref:`obeleživača "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:9
msgid "Use map canvas extent"
msgstr "Koristi obuhvat platna karte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid ""
"Draw on canvas: click and drag a rectangle delimiting the area to take into "
"account"
msgstr ""
"Nacrtaj na platnu: klikom i prevlačenjem nacrtajte pravougaonik koji "
"ograničava područje koje se uzima u obzir"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:11
msgid "Enter the coordinates as ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"
msgstr "Unesite koordinate kao ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:285
msgid "**CRS of the target raster extent**"
msgstr "**CRS ciljnog obuhvata rastera**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:288
msgid "``TARGET_EXTENT_CRS``"
msgstr "``TARGET_EXTENT_CRS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:290
msgid ""
"Specifies the CRS in which to interpret the coordinates given for the extent"
" of the output file. This must not be confused with the target CRS of the "
"output dataset. It is instead a convenience e.g. when knowing the output "
"coordinates in a geodetic long/lat CRS, but wanting a result in a projected "
"coordinate system."
msgstr ""
"Zadaje CRS u kome se tumače koordinate date za obuhvat izlazne datoteke. Ne "
"treba ga mešati sa ciljnim CRS-om izlaznog skupa podataka. To je pogodnost "
"npr. kada su izlazne koordinate poznate u geodetskom CRS-u geografske "
"dužine/širine, a rezultat se želi u projektovanom koordinatnom sistemu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:297
msgid "**Use multithreaded warping implementation**"
msgstr "**Koristi višenitnu implementaciju warp-a**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:298
msgid "``MULTITHREADING``"
msgstr "``MULTITHREADING``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterprojections.rst:302
msgid ""
"Two threads will be used to process chunks of the image and perform "
"input/output operations simultaneously. Note that the computation itself is "
"not multithreaded."
msgstr ""
"Koristiće se dve niti za obradu delova slike i istovremeno izvršavanje "
"ulazno/izlaznih operacija. Imajte na umu da samo izračunavanje nije "
"višenitno."

